The code is run using eclipse IDE platform from the following steps

1. Coding Assignment is the project created
2. Goodies is the package created
3. Main.java is the class which contains the code
4. E:\\Sanjana\\input.txt is the path that contains input file.
5. output.txt is the output file

when run button is pressed output.txt file will be generated that consists of the following output.

